rComments: Be aware that you're not taking a politics of Islam class, you're taking a history of politics in Islamic states.   2.  Different.  Things.  She herself is  fine, not super accessible, kinda dismissive.  Not sure what I learned tbh
I have such a greater appreciation for Islamic politics after taking this course. Excellent professor. So glad I took this course.

The course isn't the easiest I've ever taken, but definitely an extremely helpful and approachable professor. Classes were interesting and interactive. I'd defs recommend taking it if you're interested in the thematic focus.
